2ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Leaving%20Los%20Angeles%3A%20Why%20the%20film%20industry%20is%20ditching%20Hollywood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222389%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20O's%20of%20the%20Hollywood%20sign%20walking%20away%20with%20film%20equipment%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6733d60988cea3ba1c204b88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221195%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Nabaum%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%2010%20years%2C%20Joe%20Gallegos%20Jr.%20lived%20the%20life%20of%20an%20LA%20actor%2C%20driving%20from%20audition%20to%20audition%20across%20the%20sprawling%20city%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20landing%20a%20role.%20Things%20were%20going%20well%20%E2%80%94%20he'd%20landed%20a%20role%20in%20%26quot%3BA%20Cowgirl's%20Story%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20military%20drama%20starring%20Bailee%20Madison%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BDance%20Moms%26quot%3B%20star%20Chlo%C3%A9%20Lukasiak%2C%20and%20Pat%20Boone%2C%20and%20he%20was%20starting%20to%20read%20for%20bigger%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20all%20changed%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20when%20a%20film%20role%20brought%20him%20back%20to%20his%20native%20New%20Mexico.%20He%20was%20close%20to%20family%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20years%2C%20and%20the%20film%20industry%20there%20was%20burgeoning.%20When%20the%20movie%20wrapped%2C%20instead%20of%20sprinting%20back%20to%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Gallegos%20realized%20he%20didn't%20have%20to%20go%20back.%20The%20pandemic%20had%20shifted%20from%20in-person%20to%20on-tape.%20He's%20since%20earned%20acting%20credits%20in%20TV%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BPulse%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20medical%20procedural%20on%20Netflix%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDuster%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20JJ%20Abrams%20drama%20on%20HBO%20Max%20%E2%80%94%20both%20of%20which%20filmed%20in%20New%20Mexico.%20The%20money%20he's%20made%20from%20those%20gigs%20and%20a%20few%20independent%20projects%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20Gallegos%20to%20buy%20a%20townhouse%20in%20downtown%20Albuquerque%20%E2%80%94%20something%20he'd%20never%20come%20close%20to%20being%20able%20to%20afford%20in%20La%20La%20Land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20a%20good%20decision%20because%2C%20as%20an%20actor%2C%20I%20can%20be%20literally%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELately%2C%20creative%20workers%20are%20increasingly%20chasing%20their%20Hollywood%20dreams%20in%20production%20hubs%20far%20from%20Hollywood.%20LA%20continues%20to%20hold%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-losing-dominance-tv-movies-employment-chart-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilm%20and%20TV%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20America%2C%20but%20after%20a%20long%20grind%20of%20jobs%20slowly%20slipping%20away%2C%20the%20exodus%20from%20the%20city%20has%20accelerated%20in%20recent%20years.%20A%20recent%20analysis%20of%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20figures%20conducted%20by%20Patrick%20Adler%20and%20Taner%20Osman%20of%20Westwood%20Economics%20%26amp%3B%20Planning%20Associates%20found%20that%20the%20figure%20was%2022%25%20in%20August%2C%20down%20from%20about%2033%25%20two%20years%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what's%20making%20actors%2C%20executives%2C%20and%20studios%20look%20beyond%20the%20Hollywood%20sign%3F%20Some%20factors%20aren't%20new.%20Most%20notably%2C%20states%20have%20long%20used%20financial%20incentives%20to%20try%20to%20lure%20film%20investment%20away%20from%20California.%20But%20those%20incentives%20helped%20establish%20an%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20with%20top-notch%20sound%20stages%20being%20built%20in%20cities%20as%20varied%20as%20Dallas%2C%20Atlanta%2C%20and%20Miami%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20ready%20and%20waiting%20when%20the%20pandemic-era%20rise%20of%20remote%20work%20gave%20those%20seeking%20a%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%20a%20real%20choice%20in%20deciding%20where%20to%20live.%20Add%20it%20all%20up%2C%20and%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20glitz%20and%20glam%20of%20Hollywood%20is%20struggling%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20simple%20dollars%20and%20cents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filmed%20entertainment%20industry's%20center%20of%20gravity%20is%20shifting%20further%20from%20Hollywood%20at%20a%20time%20of%20upheaval.%20The%20decadelong%20shift%20to%20streaming%20was%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20stalled%2C%20then%20boosted%2C%20production%20as%20people%20stayed%20inside%20and%20became%20couch%20potatoes.%20Peak%20TV%20came%20to%20a%20halt%20in%202022%20when%20networks%2C%20studios%2C%20and%20streamers%20couldn't%20make%20the%20financial%20math%20for%20all%20those%20new%20streaming%20shows%20work.%20And%20filming%20was%20shut%20down%20once%20again%20in%202023%20because%20of%20the%20Hollywood%20actors%20and%20writers%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20projects%20slowly%20got%20back%20on%20their%20feet%2C%20fewer%20of%20them%20were%20turning%20their%20lights%20on%20in%20LA.%20FilmLA%2C%20which%20issues%20permits%20for%20production%20in%20the%20region%2C%20found%20that%20Greater%20Los%20Angeles'%20share%20of%20US-produced%20TV%20and%20film%20projects%20declined%20from%2023%25%20in%202021%20to%2018%25%20last%20year.%20The%20number%20of%20people%20employed%20in%20the%20traditional%20entertainment%20industry%20in%20LA%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%2C%20hit%20a%2030-year%20low%20in%20June.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20jobs%20related%20to%20video%20gaming%2C%20live%20events%2C%20and%20the%20creator%20economy%20rose%20in%20the%20city%20as%20people's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emarketer.com%2Fcontent%2Fdigital-media-makes-up-nearly-two-thirds-of-consumers-total-time-spent-with-media%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedia%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20shifted%20toward%20social%20video%20and%20away%20from%20traditional%20TV%20and%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22breakout-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FG6oF4%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Share%20of%20employment%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22487%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20reason%20that%20productions%20are%20looking%20elsewhere%20is%20cost.%20The%20wage%20gains%20made%20by%20the%20actors%20and%20writers%20have%20increased%20budgets%20for%20talent%2C%20leading%20producers%20to%20hunt%20for%20ways%20to%20drive%20down%20outlays%20in%20other%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20including%20locations.%20Thirty-seven%20states%20offer%20perks%20for%20film%20and%20TV%20production%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20in%20the%20form%20of%20tax%20credits%20equal%20to%20a%20percentage%20of%20a%20production's%20in-state%20spending%2C%20or%20cash%20rebates%20%E2%80%94%20and%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncsl.org%2Fstate-legislatures-news%2Fdetails%2Fwatch-out-hollywood-states-want-a-piece-of-the-moviemaking-action-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleast%2018%20states%20have%20implemented%20or%20expanded%3C%2Fa%3E%20film%20tax%20incentives%20since%202021.%20Georgia%20boosted%20its%20incentive%20program%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ajc.com%2Fblog%2Fbuzz%2Ftop-grossing-films-shot-georgia-since-2008%2FjoqaWPplc0L2mKzwmcNMwK%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2008%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20helping%20attract%20big-budget%20films%20like%20Disney's%20Marvel%20franchise%20and%20the%20Netflix%20hit%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things.%26quot%3B%20Atlanta's%20share%20of%20entertainment%20employment%20is%20still%20relatively%20small%20%E2%80%94%20just%202%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Otis%20Report%20on%20the%20Creative%20Economy%2C%20a%20closely-watched%20research%20study%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20has%20doubled%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20and%20shows%20no%20sign%20of%20slowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20productions%20move%20out%20of%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20it%20becomes%20easier%20for%20others%20to%20follow.%20Tiffany%20FitzHenry%2C%20an%20executive%20producer%20known%20for%20%26quot%3BSound%20of%20Hope%3A%20The%20Story%20of%20Possum%20Trot%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20seen%20the%20Atlanta%20area%20evolve%20since%20relocating%20there%20from%20LA%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20training%20for%20not%20just%20below%20the%20line%20but%20people%20in%20producing%2C%20packaging%2C%20financing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20shift%20in%20major%20studio%20movies%20to%20the%20city%20had%20brought%20with%20it%20the%20structures%20needed%20to%20sustain%20a%20more%20permanent%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20movies%20have%20been%20made%20here%20for%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20all%20the%20toys%20and%20tools%20at%20our%20fingertips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20states%20are%20getting%20in%20on%20the%20action.%20Kentucky%20passed%20an%20incentive%20program%20in%202022%20offering%20fully%20refundable%20production%20tax%20credits%20worth%20up%20to%20%2475%20million%20total%20or%20%2410%20million%20a%20project.%20Its%20second-largest%20city%2C%20Lexington%2C%20recently%20hired%20the%20entertainment%20marketer%20Lisa%20Brin%2C%20a%20Lexington%20native%2C%20to%20help%20persuade%20studios%20to%20shoot%20there.%20Brin%20said%20Lexington%20had%20attracted%2030%20film%20and%20TV%20projects%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20representing%20more%20than%20%242%20million%20in%20local%20spending.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20financial%20incentives%2C%20the%20city%20touts%20production%20spaces%20like%20Lex%20Studios%2C%20a%20facility%20with%20three%20sound%20stages%2C%20a%20growing%20crew%20base%2C%20and%20a%20willingness%20to%20pull%20strings%20as%20they%20did%20for%20a%20recent%20production%20that%20requested%20a%20major%20street%20to%20be%20closed%20for%20a%20shoot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20luring%20productions%2C%20these%20areas%20are%20also%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20more%20appealing%20for%20creatives%20to%20stick%20around%20once%20the%20cameras%20shut%20off.%20Georgia%20and%20Kentucky%20are%20among%20states%20that%20have%20invested%20in%20training%20programs%20to%20foster%20homegrown%20talent%20and%20initiatives%20like%20FilmLex%20as%20a%20resource%20hub%20to%20help%20productions.%20For%20transplants%2C%20it's%20cheaper%20to%20live%20and%20raise%20a%20family%20outside%20LA%20as%20well%20as%20New%20York%2C%20the%20second-biggest%20entertainment%20market.%20And%20while%20jobs%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20might%20be%20the%20primary%20reasons%20people%20move%2C%20the%20proliferation%20of%20cultural%20amenities%20in%20many%20smaller%20cities%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20them%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E26%20Keys%2C%20a%20production%20founded%20by%20Noah%20Hawley%2C%20an%20Austin%20native%20who%20created%20FX's%20%26quot%3BFargo%26quot%3B%20series%2C%20is%20taking%20steps%20to%20build%20up%20Austin's%20entertainment%20cultural%20capital%2C%20with%20plans%20for%20a%20library%2C%20events%20like%20industry%20happy%20hours%2C%20and%20film%20screenings%2C%20working%20with%20organizations%20like%20the%20Austin%20Film%20Society%20and%20South%20by%20Southwest.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20don't%20think%20there's%20a%20real%20sort%20of%20hub%20that's%20trying%20to%20connect%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Maddy%20Bilder%2C%20a%20project%20director%20at%2026%20Keys.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20we're%20hoping%20to%20do%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20US%20that%20are%20drawing%20film%20crews%20away%20from%20LA%3B%20other%20countries%20are%20trying%20to%20win%20over%20Hollywood%20as%20well.%20Hungary%2C%20with%20a%2020-year-old%20tax%20rebate%20and%20access%20to%20culture%20and%20an%20expanding%20stage%20system%2C%20was%20recently%20the%20setting%20for%20Yorgos%20Lanthimos'%20%26quot%3BPoor%20Things.%26quot%3B%20Australia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ausfilm.com.au%2Fmedia-releases%2Fausfilm-celebrates-passage-of-australias-30-location-offset%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20doubled%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20location%20tax%20credit%20to%2030%25%20this%20summer%20after%20big-budget%20titles%20like%20the%20Sony%20Pictures%20rom-com%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20but%20You%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Universal%20Pictures%20comedy%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fall%20Guy%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20starred%20Ryan%20Gosling%20and%20Emily%20Blunt%2C%20were%20shot%20there.%20Roughly%2060%25%20of%20Netflix's%20and%20Amazon's%20commissions%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20year%20were%20on%20continents%20other%20than%20North%20America%2C%20according%20to%20Ampere%20Analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20of%20producers%2C%20senior%20production%20people%2C%20moving%20to%20places%20like%20Australia%20or%20working%20in%20Hungary%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tyler%20Mitchell%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-ron-howard-brian-grazer-impact-production-crew-staffing-platform-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImpact%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20LinkedIn-like%20platform%20for%20Hollywood.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20the%20governments%20have%20supported%20a%20lot%20of%20education%2C%20training%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20as%20they%20built%20up%20production%20facilities%2C%20they%20had%20enough%20crew%20to%20service%20sound%20stages.%20So%20there%20is%20more%20of%20a%20talent%20base%20globally%20in%20places%20like%20Ireland%2C%20Budapest%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20the%20UK.%20I've%20heard%20of%20more%20productions%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20looking%20for%20crew%20than%20I%20ever%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActually%20being%20on%20a%20set%20is%20only%20one%20part%20of%20entertainment%20production.%20Development%2C%20preproduction%2C%20and%20postproduction%20are%20responsible%20for%20a%20huge%20portion%20of%20what%20ends%20up%20on%20screen.%20But%20here%2C%20too%2C%20the%20need%20to%20physically%20be%20in%20the%20mecca%20of%20moviemaking%20is%20waning.%20Technology%20is%20giving%20rise%20to%20a%20Tinseltown%20version%20of%20remote%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelf-tapes%2C%20where%20actors%20use%20ring%20lights%20and%20film%20themselves%20at%20home%20to%20connect%20with%20casting%20directors%2C%20have%20become%20commonplace.%20Many%20meetings%20to%20pitch%20projects%20that%20shifted%20to%20Zoom%20early%20in%20the%20pandemic%20have%20stayed%20on%20video.%20On%20the%20postproduction%20side%2C%20file%20sharing%20and%20editing%20platforms%20like%20Pix%20and%20ScreenIt%20Pro%20enable%20production%20companies%20like%2026%20Keys%20to%20review%20content%20locally%20rather%20than%20fly%20to%20editing%20rooms%20in%20LA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20pitch%20meetings%20are%20happening%20over%20Zoom%2C%20four%20years%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20Bilder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20power%20of%20Los%20Angeles%20is%20dispersing%2C%20no%20single%20%26quot%3Bnew%20Hollywood%26quot%3B%20is%20coming%20to%20take%20its%20place.%20The%20end%20of%20Peak%20TV%20has%20contracted%20employment%20all%20over%20%E2%80%94%20the%20total%20number%20of%20jobs%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-losing-dominance-tv-movies-employment-chart-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20447%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20declined%209.1%25%20from%202013%20to%202024.%20Even%20as%20markets%20like%20Atlanta%20and%20Miami%20grow%2C%20their%20homegrown%20entertainment%20encampments%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20match%20the%20hundred-year%20history%20of%20LA%20%E2%80%94%20the%20most%20valuable%20parts%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%2C%20like%20casting%20big%20stars%2C%20greenlighting%2C%20and%20packaging%2C%20are%20still%20concentrated%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20high%20stakes%20there.%20This%20is%20an%20area%20where%20trust%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adler%2C%20the%20principal%20at%20Westwood%2C%20which%20conducted%20research%20for%20the%20Otis%20report.%20%26quot%3BYou%20built%20it%20through%20face-to-face%20interaction%2C%20repeated%20exchanges.%20That's%20why%20casting%20for%20top%20roles%20still%20happens%20in%20LA%2C%20even%20if%20they%20end%20up%20being%20shot%20elsewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20are%20just%20starting%20out%20or%20who%20work%20on%20the%20creative%20side%2C%20too%2C%20Hollywood%20is%20still%20where%20careers%20are%20made%20and%20nurtured.%20FitzHenry%20wishes%20there%20were%20more%20directors%20and%20producers%20with%20packaging%20and%20marketing%20skills%20in%20Georgia.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20skill%20set%20that%20hasn't%20been%20outside%20of%20Hollywood%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BCurrently%2C%20the%20only%20way%20to%20learn%20is%20for%20a%20producer%20to%20adopt%20and%20teach%20you.%20I%20was%20lucky%20to%20work%20with%20highly%20skilled%20producers%2C%20which%20I%20learned%20in%20LA%2C%20like%20an%20oral%20tradition.%20That's%20a%20lot%20of%20relational%20capital%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20established.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeisha%20Perry%2C%20a%20longtime%20entertainment%20attorney%20in%20Atlanta%20whose%20clients%20have%20included%20Cedric%20the%20Entertainer's%20production%20company%20and%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BThe%20Waterboyz%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20that%20being%20a%20local%20attorney%20had%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20growing%20number%20of%20productions%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20South%20but%20that%20she%20still%20traveled%20to%20LA%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20decision-makers%20are%20in%20LA%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20those%20people%20who%20feel%20as%20though%20if%20you're%20not%20in%20LA%2C%20your%20legitimacy%20can%20be%20questioned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%20evidence%20of%20LA's%20staying%20power%20is%20in%20the%20industries%20like%20video%20games%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20the%20creator%20economy%20that%20are%20concentrated%20there%20because%20of%20the%20city's%20legacy%20in%20entertainment%2C%20which%20has%20endured%20through%20the%20rise%20of%20radio%2C%20then%20TV%2C%20then%20streaming.%20That%20may%20not%20necessarily%20lead%20to%20more%20TV%20shows%20and%20films%20being%20made%20there%2C%20but%20it%20underscores%20The%20Town's%20cultural%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGallegos%20estimates%20that%20he%20still%20gets%20half%20his%20work%20from%20outside%20New%20Mexico%2C%20helped%20by%20representation%20he%20has%20in%20LA.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%2C%20major%20roles%20are%20not%20cast%20here%20and%20often%20not%20shot%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20For%20all%20the%20perks%2C%20he%20misses%20the%20excitement%20of%20being%20in%20LA.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20stuff%20happening%2024%2F7.%20I'm%20a%20trained%20dancer%2C%20too.%20I%20could%20always%20jump%20into%20something.%26quot%3B%20Then%20there's%20the%20nagging%20feeling%20that%20virtual%20auditions%20don't%20count.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20I%20think%20I'm%20sending%20things%20out%20into%20the%20void%20that%20don't%20get%20watched.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20similar%20professional%20gaps%20she%20sees%2C%20FitzHenry%20remains%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20Atlanta.%20She's%20found%20an%20affordable%2C%20friendly%20place%20to%20raise%20her%20kids%20and%20a%20tight-knit%20professional%20community%20that%20pulls%20together%20to%20help%20bring%20projects%20to%20the%20state%2C%20things%20she%20never%20experienced%20in%20LA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20sense%20people%20really%20care%20about%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20used%20to%20be%20that%20mentality%20of%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20in%20Hollywood%20to%20be%20in%20the%20business.%20I%20think%20that's%20changing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flucia-moses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELucia%20Moses%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20covering%20the%20intersection%20of%20tech%20and%20Hollywood%20for%20Business%20Insider's%20Media%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-leaving-los-angeles-remote-work-tv-movies-money-streaming-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731578581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6733d5c388cea3ba1c204b77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-leaving-los-angeles-remote-work-tv-movies-money-streaming-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20share%20of%20productions%20being%20shot%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20is%20on%20the%20decline.%20That's%20allowing%20entertainment%20workers%20to%20move%20across%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-leaving-los-angeles-remote-work-tv-movies-money-streaming-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20seen%20rescuing%20trapped%20children%20in%20Valencia%20floods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731578524000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7f85%2Flive%2F8295c060-a26a-11ef-bdf5-b7cb2fa86e10.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcvgep3exwq7o%234%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20man%20and%20four%20children%2C%20including%20his%20daughter%2C%20were%20trapped%20inside%20at%20a%20English%20language%20school.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcvgep3exwq7o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3