C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt%20Will%20Be%20Retirement...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-Aus%20Skipper's%20Explosive%20Take%20On%20Rohit-Virat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Australian%20cricketer%20Michael%20Clarke%20expressed%20that%20if%20star%20India%20batters%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20fail%20to%20perform%20during%20the%20upcoming%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20they%20could%20retire%20from%20the%20format.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20the%20first%20Test%20set%20to%20take%20place%20at%20Perth%20from%20November%2022%20onwards%2C%20two%20Indian%20veterans%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20a%20make-or-break%20BGT%20series%20after%20a%20horrific%20home%20season%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand.%20Speaking%20at%20ESPN's%20Around%20the%20Wicket%20podcast%2C%20Clarke%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20is%20their%20last%20time%20here%20in%20Australia%2C%20I%20think%20it%20will%20be%20retirement.%20They%20would%20not%20be%20dropped%2C%20but%20in%20the%20same%20breath%2C%20I%20think%20every%20cricketer%20knows%20that%20if%20you%20are%20not%20making%20runs%20or%20taking%20wickets%2C%20there%20will%20be%20conversations%20around%20that%20kind%20of%20a%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20team%2C%20you%20get%20a%20slack%20for%20that%2C%20and%20if%20you%20are%20the%20world's%20best%20batter%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%20-%20maybe%20longer%20-%20across%20formats%2C%20I%20think%20Virat%20may%20get%20a%20bit%20more%20slack%20than%20somebody%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20for%20this%20series'%20sake%2C%20Test%20cricket's%20sakes%2C%20they%20both%20come%20out%2C%20get%20back%20to%20their%20best%20form%20and%20score%20plenty%20of%20runs%20for%20India%2C%20but%20also%20Test%20cricket.%20We%20want%20to%20see%20the%20Australian%20attack%20which%20is%20a%20good%20one%2C%20take%20on%20the%20top-order%20batting%20of%20India%20which%20is%20pretty%20strong%20in%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli's%20recent%20statistics%20are%20far%20from%20encouraging.%20His%20struggles%20against%20spin%20have%20worsened%2C%20scoring%20only%20192%20runs%20in%2010%20innings%20across%20five%20Tests%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%2C%20averaging%20just%2021.33%2C%20with%20one%20fifty%20and%20a%20best%20score%20of%2070.%20His%20scores%20in%20the%20recent%20home%20season%20were%3A%206%2C%2017%2C%2047%2C%2029*%2C%200%2C%2070%2C%201%2C%2017%2C%204%2C%20and%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Kohli%20has%20accumulated%20just%20250%20runs%20in%2012%20Test%20innings%20across%20six%20matches%2C%20averaging%2022.72%2C%20with%20one%20half-century%20and%20a%20top%20score%20of%2070.%20However%2C%20he%20has%20shown%20better%20form%20in%20away%20tours%20to%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20scoring%20561%20runs%20in%20the%20ongoing%20WTC%20cycle%202023-25%2C%20with%20a%20century%2C%20three%20fifties%2C%20and%20a%20best%20score%20of%20121%20across%20nine%20Tests%20and%2016%20innings%2C%20averaging%2037.40.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit's%20recent%20numbers%20are%20also%20underwhelming.%20Across%20five%20Tests%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20he%20scored%20133%20runs%20in%2010%20innings%2C%20averaging%20only%2013.30%2C%20with%20a%20best%20score%20of%2052.%20His%20scores%20in%20the%20home%20season%20were%3A%206%2C%205%2C%2023%2C%208%2C%202%2C%2052%2C%200%2C%208%2C%2018%2C%20and%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Rohit%20has%20managed%20588%20runs%20in%2011%20Tests%20and%2021%20innings%2C%20averaging%2029.40%2C%20with%20two%20centuries%2C%20two%20fifties%2C%20and%20a%20top%20score%20of%20131.%20In%20the%20ongoing%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%202023-25%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20833%20runs%20in%2014%20Tests%20at%20an%20average%20of%2033.32%2C%20with%20three%20centuries%20and%20four%20fifties%2C%20his%20best%20score%20being%20131.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20much-anticipated%20Border-Gavaskar%20series%20between%20India%20and%20Australia%20kicks%20off%20on%20November%2022%2C%20with%20the%20first%20Test%20at%20Perth.%20The%20second%20Test%2C%20featuring%20the%20day-night%20format%2C%20will%20take%20place%20under%20lights%20at%20Adelaide%20Oval%20from%20December%206%20to%2010.%20Fans%20will%20then%20turn%20their%20attention%20to%20The%20Gabba%20in%20Brisbane%20for%20the%20third%20Test%20from%20December%2014%20to%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%2C%20scheduled%20from%20December%2026%20to%2030%20at%20Melbourne's%20iconic%20Melbourne%20Cricket%20Ground%2C%20will%20mark%20the%20series'%20penultimate%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fifth%20and%20final%20Test%20will%20be%20held%20at%20the%20Sydney%20Cricket%20Ground%20from%20January%203%20to%207%2C%20promising%20an%20exciting%20climax%20to%20a%20highly%20anticipated%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731576780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Ftk6rehcg_virat-kohli-rohit-sharma_625x300_08_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fit-will-be-retirement-ex-australia-skippers-explosive-take-on-rohit-sharma-virat-kohli-7013395%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michael%20Clarke%20expressed%20that%20if%20star%20India%20batters%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20fail%20to%20perform%20during%20the%20upcoming%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20they%20could%20retire%20from%20the%20format.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAgainst%20Bureaucracy%20Back%20Then%20Too%26quot%3B%3A%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20Reacts%20To%20Viral%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian-American%20entrepreneur%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20on%20Wednesday%20reacted%20to%