ad%20%26quot%3Bburied%20his%20feelings%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20Congress's%20%26quot%3Bvotebank%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20days%20Khargeji%20is%20getting%20angry%20with%20me...%20Khargeji%2C%20don't%20get%20angry%20at%20me.%20I%20respect%20your%20age.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20get%20angry...%20get%20angry%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20Nizam.%20The%20Nizam's%20'razakars'%20burnt%20your%20village%2C%20brutally%20killed%20Hindus%2C%20and%20burnt%20your%20respected%20mother%2C%20sister%2C%20and%20family%20members.%20Present%20this%20truth%20before%20the%20country%20-%20whenever%20they%20will%20be%20divided%2C%20they%20will%20be%20divided%20in%20the%20same%20brutal%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20village%20was%20under%20the%20Nizam%20of%20Hyderabad...%20when%20India%20was%20under%20the%20British.%20There%20was%20a%20fire...%20this%20was%20when%20Hindus%20were%20being%20selectively%20killed.%20And%2C%20in%20this%20fire%2C%20his%20home%20was%20also%20burned%20down%2C%20in%20which%20his%20mother%20and%20family%20were%20killed.%20But%20Khargeji%20does%20not%20say%20this...%20because%20he%20knows%20if%20he%20says%20it%2C%20then%20Muslim%20votes%20will%20shift.%20He%20forgot%20the%20sacrifice%20of%20his%20family%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Kharge's%20son%20Priyank%20said%20his%20father%20narrowly%20escaped%20death%20during%20that%20tragic%20incident%20and%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%209-time%20MLA%2C%20an%20MP%2C%20a%20Union%20Minister%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20a%20Congress%20president.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20tragedy%2C%20he%20never%20exploited%20it%20for%20political%20gain%2C%20never%20played%20the%20victim%20card%20and%20never%20let%20hatred%20define%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20K