reate%20a%20toxic%20environment%20or%20explode.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221476%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Polaris%20Dawn%20spacesuits%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67338b1b192f52589857e512%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221326%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20suits%20have%20a%20flame-resistant%20outer%20layer%20and%20thermal%20garment%20material%20to%20regulate%20temperature.%3Cp%3Escreenshot%2FPolaris%20Program%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERe-entry%20into%20Earth's%20atmosphere%2C%20even%20with%20the%20prep%20and%20training%20from%20SpaceX%2C%20remained%20a%20point%20of%20nervousness.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20problematic%20amount%20of%20debris%20damage%20to%20the%20heat%20shield%20or%20thermal%20protection%20systems%2C%20there's%20%26quot%3Bno%20backup%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaacman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20that%20while%20he%20and%20his%20family%20recognize%20the%20risks%2C%20they%20keep%20the%20mindset%20that%20it's%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2203e7aad8-03e7-44a4-8f3c-2af59a1d5fea%5C%22%3EHe's%20going%20back%20%E2%80%94%20and%20expects%20breakthroughs%20are%20'right%20around%20the%20corner'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20he%20landed%20back%20on%20Earth%2C%20Isaacman%20went%20through%20about%20three%20days%20of%20medical%20tests%20before%20largely%20resuming%20business%20as%20usual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20been%20on%20the%20road%20a%20lot%2C%20visiting%20facilities%20and%20doing%20debriefs%2C%20and%20estimates%20he's%20only%20slept%20in%20his%20bed%20four%20or%20five%20times%20since%20his%20journey%20to%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsaacman%20has%20maintained%20his%20role%20as%20CEO%2C%20which%20he%20said%20helps%20make%20his%20work%20with%20St.%20Jude%20and%20SpaceX%20possible.%20Isaacman%20funded%20both%20Polaris%20Dawn%20and%20his%20previous%20mission%20with%20SpaceX.%20The%20first%20mission%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopene