20is%20played%20by%20a%20total%20of%2012%20nations%2C%20a%20clash%20between%20the%20Number%201%20(Australia)%20and%20Number%202%20(India)%20teams%2C%20and%20that%20too%20on%20mostly%20fiery%20Aussie%20pitches%2C%20is%20a%20main%20course%20to%20drool%20over.%20Add%20to%20that%20the%20statistical%20hors%20d'oeuvres%20of%20India%20having%20won%20the%20last%20four%20versions%20of%20this%20rivalry%20(2016-2023)%2C%20including%20back-to-back%20historic%20series%20wins%20the%20last%20two%20times%20they%20toured%20Kangaroo%20Land%2C%20and%20you%20have%20yourself%20a%20meal%20to%20die%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20High-Stakes%20Game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20don't%20be%20surprised%20though%20if%20the%20five-match%20series%20breaks%20all%20viewership%20records.%20After%20all%2C%20this%20enticing%20meal%20also%20has%20the%20added%20spice%20of%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20two%20batting%20Titans%20of%20the%20sport%2C%20perhaps%20playing%20their%20last%20series%20Down%20Under.%20But%20that%20is%20not%20what%20will%20make%20the%20biggest%20headlines.%20Those%20will%20undoubtedly%20be%20reserved%20for%20their%20performances%20with%20the%20bat.%20After%20all%2C%20there%20is%20very%20little%20doubt%20that%20the%20number%20of%20runs%20these%20two%20players%20end%20up%20scoring%20and%20how%20big%20an%20impact%20they%20have%20on%20positive%20results%20for%20their%20team%20will%20determine%20how%20many%20miles%20there%20are%20still%20left%20in%20their%20Test%20journeys.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20the%20upcoming%20series%20is%20an%20extremely%20important%20one%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20team%20overall%20and%20for%20these%20two%20stalwarts%20of%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20along%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20%E2%80%98super%20seniors'%20like%20R.%20Ashwin%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja.%20The%20entire%20cricketing%20fraternity%20will%20be%20watching%20very%2C%20very%20closely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20begs%20the%20question%E2%80%94what%20will%20happen%2C%20realistically%2C%20if%20Virat%20and%20Rohit's%20bats%20are%20largely%20silent%20in%20Australia%20this%20time%2C%20just%20like%20they%20were%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20then%20New%20Zealand%2C%20when%20India%20were%20whitewashed%200-3%20at%20home%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20Test%20series%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20and%20Rohit%2C%20who%20are%20synonymous%20with%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20have%20over%20the%20years%20been%20tagged%20by%20many%20as%20rivals%2C%20adversaries%20and%20competitors.%20Right%20now%2C%20however%2C%20they%20find%20themselves%20in%20the%20same%20boat%2C%20trying%20to%20weather%20the%20same%20storm%2C%20with%20time%20running%20out.%20The%20two%20also%20found%20themselves%20right%20next%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20run%20charts%20of%20the%20recent%20Test%20series%20vs%20the%20Kiwis%2C%20as%20Numbers%2012%20and%2013%2C%20respectively.%20Virat%20scored%2093%20runs%20in%20six%20innings%20and%20Rohit%20scored%2091.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDawn%20Of%20The%20Young%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20athlete%20wants%20to%20go%20out%20on%20a%20low%E2%80%94especially%20not%20Virat%20and%20Rohit%2C%20who%20we%20saw%20bowing%20out%20big%20when%20they%20announced%20their%20T20%20international%20retirements%20right%20after%20India%20won%20the%20last%20edition%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20They%20knew%20that%20the%20second%2C%20even%20third-rung%20players%2C%20were%20more%20or%20less%20fully%20baked%E2%80%94especially%20in%20the%20shortest%20format%20of%20the%20game%E2%80%94with%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20young%20talent%20ready%20to%20break%20down%20the%20senior%20team%20door.%20Similar%20thoughts%20must%20be%20running%20in%20their%20heads%20right%20now%20ahead%20of%20the%20Test%20series%20with%20the%20Aussies.%20Change%20is%20already%20imminent.%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20has%20a%20century%20and%20three%20fifties%20in%20the%20six%20Tests%20he%20has%20played%20so%20far.%20Abhimanyu%20Easwaran%2C%20a%20First-Class%20legend%20for%20Bengal%2C%20is%20itching%20to%20make%20his%20Test%20debut.%20Dhruv%20Jurel%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20Kargil%20war%20veteran%2C%20recently%20averaged%2074%20in%20two%20innings%20for%20India%20A%20in%20the%20second%20unofficial%20Test%20against%20Australia%20A%2C%20with%20scores%20of%2080%20and%2068.%20All%20three%20are%20in%20the%20India%20squad%20for%20the%20series%20against%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20and%20Rohit's%20biggest%20priority%20right%20now%20will%20be%20to%20prove%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%94and%20perhaps%20to%20themselves%2C%20too%E2%80%94that%20they%20can%20still%20convert%20the%20hunger%20in%20their%20bellies%20to%20Test%20runs%20on%20the%20board.%20They%20have%20to%20do%20that%20against%20the%20top-ranked%20team%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20both%20in%20the%20Test%20rankings%20and%20on%20the%202023-25%20WTC%20cycle%20points%20table%2C%20and%2C%20that%20too%2C%20in%20their%20own%20den.%20The%20head%20curator%20of%20Western%20Australia%20cricket%20has%20promised%20that%20the%20drop-in%20pitch%20for%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Perth%20will%20have%20great%20pace%20and%20bounce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Australia%20Is%20A%20Litmus%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20short%20of%20a%20litmus%20test%20awaits%20the%20duo.%20Virat%20for%20one%20will%20take%20confidence%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20has%20a%20very%20good%20record%20on%20Aussie%20shores%E2%80%94an%20average%20of%20over%2054%20in%2013%20Tests%2C%20with%20a%20highest%20score%20of%20169%20and%20overall%2C%20six%20centuries.%20This%20might%20just%20be%20the%20perfect%20setting%20for%20him%20to%20roar%20back%20to%20form.%20Rohit's%20batting%20average%20in%20Australia%2C%2031.38%2C%20is%20not%20great%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20too%20bad%20either.%20He%20is%20yet%20to%20score%20a%20century%20Down%20Under.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20secret%20that%20at%2036%20and%2037%2C%20respectively%2C%20Virat%20and%20Rohit%20are%20in%20the%20twilight%20of%20their%20careers.%20Both%20would%20have%20given%20serious%20thought%20to%20Test%20retirement%20and%20set%20rough%20timelines%20and%20goals.%20Remember%2C%20Test%20cricket%20is%20also%20the%20most%20physically%20demanding%20format.%20Also%2C%20there's%20no%20doubt%20that%20they%20would%20have%20both%20fantasised%20about%20helping%20India%20win%20the%20ICC%20WTC%20Final%20at%20Lord's%20in%20June%20next%20year%2C%20something%20the%20team%20hasn't%20managed%20to%20do%20yet%20despite%20being%20finalists%20in%20both%20the%20completed%20editions%20so%20far%20(2019-21%20and%202021-23).%20Apart%20from%20beating%20the%20Aussies%20in%20their%20own%20backyard%20for%20the%20third%20straight%20time%2C%20there%20is%20also%20the%20added%20incentive%20now%20of%20qualifying%20for%20that%20final%20(though%20India%20need%20to%20win%204-0%20to%20qualify%20on%20their%20own).%20The%20final%20outcome%20of%20that%20pursuit%20could%20also%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20determining%20Virat%20and%20Rohit's%20Test%20futures.%20If%20all%20the%20pieces%20fall%20into%20place%2C%20it%20could%20well%20be%20the%20perfect%20time%20for%20them%20to%20bring%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20their%20Test%20careers%2C%20silence%20the%20critics%2C%20and%20then%20leave%20nothing%20to%20chance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEngland%20Is%20Beckoning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20here's%20the%20catch%E2%80%94the%20big%20difference%20this%20time%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20last%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20when%20they%20chose%20to%20ride%20into%20the%20international%20T20%20sunset%20on%20a%20high%2C%20is%20that%20if%20they%20manage%20to%20bounce%20back%20hard%20in%20Australia%20and%20play%20a%20series-defining%20knocks%2C%20it%20perhaps%20won't%20be%20that%20easy%20for%20them%20to%20take%20the%20call%20to%20end%20their%20Test%20careers.%20There's%20another%20high-profile%20Test%20series%20on%20foreign%20soil%20coming%20up%20in%20about%20seven%20months%2C%20with%20India%20scheduled%20to%20tour%20England%20for%20a%20five-Test%20series%20from%20June%20to%20August%20of%202025.%20That%20is%20too%20tempting%20a%20chance%20to%20miss%2C%20especially%20at%20this%20stage%20of%20their%20careers.%20They%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20are%20very%20much%20in%20the%20mix%20when%20the%20squad%20for%20that%20tour%20is%20picked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20perhaps%20that%20it's%20now%20or%20never%20for%20both%20star%20batters%2C%20because%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20both%20these%20senior%20players%20would%20like%20to%20avoid%20like%20the%20plague%20is%20the%20ignominy%20of%20being%20dropped%20by%20the%20selectors.%20And%20that%20is%20a%20real%20possibility%20if%20they%20don't%20get%20at%20least%20a%20few%20big%20scores%20each%20and%20if%20the%20team%20overall%20doesn't%20do%20well.%20BCCI%20sources%20have%20been%20quoted%20as%20saying%20that%20they%20will%20not%20be%20on%20the%20flight%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20play%20England%20if%20India%20fail%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20WTC%20Final.%20At%20home%2C%20in%20the%20series%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Virat's%20average%20in%2010%20innings%20was%20under%2023%2C%20while%20Rohit's%20was%2013.30.TC%20Final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20Write%20The%20Champions%20Off%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20these%20calculations%20though%2C%20let's%20not%20forget%20that%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20are%20titans%20of%20the%20sport.%20You%20can%20count%20them%20out%2C%20sure%2C%20but%20only%20at%20your%20own%20peril.%20Head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%20while%20describing%20the%20two%20batters%20as%20%E2%80%98incredibly%20tough%20men'%2C%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20convey%20the%20message%20that%20the%20two%20are%20still%20very%20%E2%80%98hungry'.%20It's%20the%20same%20hunger%20that%20saw%20a%20certain%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20silence%20his%20critics%20after%202003%2C%20when%20his%20Test%20average%20dropped%20to%2017%2C%20and%20then%20again%20around%202005-2007%2C%20when%20critics%20said%20that%20it%20was%20time%20for%20him%20to%20hang%20up%20his%20boots.%20Michael%20Hussey%20recently%20talked%20about%20how%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Csilly%E2%80%9D%20to%20write%20off%20champion%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20some%20might%20also%20argue%20that%20things%20are%20different%20now.%20Star%20value%20matters%2C%20but%20questions%20are%20asked.%20Gambhir%20himself%20has%20said%20that%20he%20wants%20his%20players%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98absolutely%20selfless'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%20though%2C%20everything%20is%20likely%20to%20boil%20down%20to%20a%20few%20very%20simple%20questions%E2%80%94were%20there%20any%20ultimatums%20given%20in%20the%20chat%20that%20the%20BCCI%2C%20the%20chief%20selector%2C%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20and%20the%20coach%20had%20with%20Rohit%20after%20the%20New%20Zealand%20series%20debacle%3F%20If%20the%20two%20star%20players%20do%20fail%20in%20Australia%20and%20are%20still%20kept%20in%20the%20mix%2C%20how%20prepared%20are%20the%20Indian%20Board%20and%20the%20coach%20to%20weather%20the%20storm%20of%20the%20inevitable%20public%20outcry%3F%20And%2C%20the%20most%20important%20of%20questions%3A%20what%20exactly%20are%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20themselves%20feeling%20in%20their%20bones%20right%20now%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20thing%20you%20can%20bet%20on%20is%20that%20neither%20player%20would%20want%20to%20be%20pushed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731570840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F9m97vcn_virat-rohit_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcricket-ind-