ital.%20However%2C%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20confirmed%20that%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP%203)%20will%20not%20be%20imposed%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%20two%20days%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20season%2C%20AQI%20has%20gone%20above%20400%20in%20Delhi.%20Many%20people%20have%20questions%20in%20their%20minds%20about%20why%20the%20AQI%20which%20was%20in%20the%20'poor'%20or%20'very%20poor'%20category%20since%20October%2014%20suddenly%20went%20into%20the%20'severe'%20category.%20Meteorologists%20have%20reported%20that%20due%20to%20snowfall%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20a%20drop%20in%20the%20temperature%20of%20Delhi%20has%20been%20recorded.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20dry%20conditions%20have%20been%20created%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20evening%20in%20the%20entirety%20of%20North%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rai%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%2C%20Delhi's%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20was%20measured%20at%20428%20at%209%20am%2C%20placing%20it%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category.%20Of%20Delhi's%2039%20monitoring%20stations%2C%2032%20recorded%20AQI%20levels%20over%20400%2C%20including%20Anand%20Vihar%2C%20IGI%20Airport%2C%20Mandir%20Marg%2C%20and%20Patparganj.%20This%20marks%20Delhi's%20worst%20air%20quality%20reading%20of%20the%20season%20and%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20a%2024-hour%20AQI%20of%20418%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20an%20increase%20from%20334%20the%20day%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20improvement%20in%20the%20pollution%20level%20from%20tomorrow%2C%20due%20to%20which%20Grap%203%20is%20not%20being%20imposed%20in%20Delhi.%20Today%20we%20are%20again%20giving%20instructions%20that%20the%20rules%20made%20under%20Grap%202%20should%20be%20followed%20on%20the%20ground%20so%20that%20Grap%203%20does%20not%20have%20to%20be%20implemented.%20If%20the%20pollution%20again%20goes%20into%20the%20'severe'%20category%20then%20the%20Delhi%20government%20will%20take%20all%20the%20necessary%20steps%20and%20will%20work%20together%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rai%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeather%20reports%20show%20that%20Delhi's%20minimum%20temperature%20dipped%20to%20a%20seasonal%20low%20of%2016.1%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20around%20three%20degrees%20above%20normal.%20Smog%20in%20the%20capital%20also%20caused%20visibility%20issues%2C%20affecting%20some%20flight%20operations%20at%20Delhi%20Airport%2C%20though%20conditions%20slightly%20improved%20on%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20with%20visibility%20recorded%20at%20400%20meters%20by%208%3A30%20am.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20agreed%20to%20expedite%20a%20hearing%20on%20measures%20to%20combat%20the%20city's%20hazardous%20pollution%20levels%20on%20November%2018.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731569340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F80gjhtco_delhi-air-quality_625x300_31_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-no-grap-3-for-now-says-minister-7016409%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi's%20air%20quality%20remained%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category%20for%20a%20second%20day%20on%20Thursday%2C%20with%20low%20wind%20speed%20contributing%20to%20a%20thick%20fog%20layer%20across%20the%20national%20capital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-no-grap-3-for-now-says-minister-7016409%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sri%20Lanka%20snap%20elections%3A%20What%E2%80%99s%20at%20stake%20for%20the%20island%20nation%20dealing%20with%20economic%20crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731569046000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-11528