nst%20Australia%20starting%20November%2022.%20Virat%20has%20historically%20enjoyed%20a%20brilliant%20run%20of%20form%20in%20Australia%20and%20fans%20are%20always%20excited%20to%20see%20the%20batter%20in%20action.%20Virat%20arrived%20in%20Perth%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20match%20and%20started%20practice%20at%20the%20WACA%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20India%20hosted%20their%20first%20full-fledged%20training%20session.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewest.com.au%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Findian-megastar-virat-kohli-emerges-in-perth-for-first-hit-ahead-of-border-gavaskar-trophy-series-c-16741843%5C%22%3E%20The%20West%20Australian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fans%20climbed%20trees%20and%20some%20even%20came%20with%20their%20own%20ladders%20to%20catch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20Virat.%20The%20report%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20batter%20looked%20at%20ease%20against%20the%20fast%20bowlers%20and%20even%20played%20some%20good%20shots%20off%20their%20bowling%20before%20moving%20to%20spin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20management%20has%20decided%20to%20allow%20the%20public%20to%20watch%20their%20centre-wicket%20training%20sessions%20from%20Friday%20to%20Sunday%20when%20they%20would%20do%20match%20simulation%20and%20play%20a%20warm-up%20game%20against%20India%20A%20at%20the%20WACA%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20in%20contrary%20to%20an%20Australian%20media%20report%20claiming%20that%20the%20visiting%20team's%20practice%20sessions%20are%20closed%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20'The%20Australian'%20claimed%20in%20a%20report%20that%20a%20team%20of%20construction%20workers%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20refurbishing%20the%20WACA%2C%20has%20been%20mailed%20by%20its%20company%20CEO%20to%20not%20watch%2C%20click%20pictures%2C%20or%20fly%20drones%20during%20the%20India%20net%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20extent%20to%20which%20India%20is%20keeping%20their%20practice%20guarded%20is%20laid%20bare%20in%