20mother%20of%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20autopsy%20report%20said%20samples%20to%20check%20for%20sex%20assault%20could%20not%20be%20taken%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20body%20parts%20were%20completely%20charred%20and%20not%20recognisable.%26quot%3B%20The%20family%20has%20buried%20the%20body%20after%20performing%20the%20last%20rites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20The%20right%20upper%20limb%20and%20parts%20of%20both%20lower%20limbs%20and%20the%20facial%20structure%20%5Bwere%5D%20found%20missing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20penetrating%20wound%20of%20size%201%20cm%20x%200.75%20cm%20%5Bis%5D%20seen%20over%20the%20back%20of%20the%20right%20thigh...%20coming%20out%20through%20an%20opening%20measuring%202%20cm%20x%201%20cm%20in%20the%20right%20upper%20thigh...%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20mortem%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20a%205-cm-long%20metallic%20nail%20was%20found%20embedded%20on%20the%20left%20thigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBurnt%20and%20separated%20fragments%20of%20bone%20did%20not%20show%20any%20signs%20of%20vital%20reaction%20indicating%20the%20post%20mortem%20nature%20of%20separation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20autopsy%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20autopsy%20was%20done%20at%20Silchar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20neighbouring%20Assam%2C%20two%20days%20after%20the%20woman%20was%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeath%20was%20due%20to%20shock%20as%20a%20result%20of%20third-degree%20mixed%20flame%20antemortem%20burns%20as%20described%20which%20covered%2099%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20body%20surface%20area.%20Time%20since%20death%20was%2024%20to%2036%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20autopsy%20report%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20husband%20in%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20filed%20with%20the%20police%20in%20Jiribam%2C%20120%20km%20from%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%2C%20had%20alleged%20she%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20leg%20when%20th