ntitrust%20enforcement%2C%20particularly%20against%20companies%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Alphabet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20internet's%20hall%20monitors%20out%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20they%20think%20they%20can%20suppress%20us%2C%20discourage%20us.%20Maybe%20if%20you're%20just%20a%20little%20less%20patriotic.%20Maybe%20if%20you%20just%20conform%20to%20their%20way%20of%20thinking%20a%20little%20more%2C%20then%20you'll%20be%20allowed%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20digital%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaetz%20said%20during%20a%202021%20appearance%20shortly%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-trump-bans-from-twitter-facebook-dont-violate-first-amendment-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20had%20been%20banned%20from%20social%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-trump-bans-from-twitter-facebook-dont-violate-first-amendment-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedia%20platforms%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20January%206%20insurrection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20you%20know%20what%3F%20Silicon%20Valley%20can't%20cancel%20this%20movement%2C%20or%20this%20rally%2C%20or%20this%20congressman%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20audience.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20Second%20Amendment%20in%20this%20country%2C%20and%20I%20think%20we%20have%20an%20obligation%20to%20use%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20unclear%20how%20much%20his%20appointment%20to%20attorney%20general%2C%20if%20approved%20by%20the%20Senate%2C%20would%20impact%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20the%20congressman%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Justice%20Department%20and%20the%20FTC%20are%20responsible%20for%20enforcing%20antitrust%20laws%20in%20the%20US.%20Current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftc-chair-lina-khan-60-minutes-americans-