2%3EAI%20adoption%20is%20plateauing%20among%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-business-execs-trending-insights-ai-worker-well-being-roundtable-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20staying%20a%20priority%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20many%20executives%2C%20with%2099%25%20surveyed%20saying%20they%20will%20invest%20in%20AI%20this%20year%2C%20desk%20worker%20enthusiasm%20is%20decelerating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20excitement%20rates%20about%20AI%20have%20dropped%20six%20percentage%20points%20globally%20over%20the%20past%20three%20months.%20In%20particular%2C%20the%20number%20of%20US%20workers%20who%20said%20they're%20%26quot%3Bexcited%20about%20AI%20helping%20them%20to%20complete%20tasks%20at%20work%26quot%3B%20dropped%20from%2045%25%20to%2036%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20also%20saw%20its%20AI%20adoption%20rates%20increase%20by%20only%20a%20single%20percentage%20point%2C%20from%2032%25%20to%2033%25%20among%20desk%20workers.%20In%20the%20report%2C%20Christina%20Janzer%2C%20head%20of%20Slack's%20Workforce%20Lab%2C%20said%20that%20the%20stalling%20growth%20in%20AI%20usage%20and%20interest%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Breal%20wakeup%20call%26quot%3B%20for%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c34dd29b-e70c-45d2-90d9-ed48f693f888%5C%22%3EAround%20half%20surveyed%20don't%20want%20to%20tell%20their%20manager%20they%20use%20AI%20at%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20daily%20work%20tasks%20like%20writing%20messages%20or%20brainstorming%20ideas%2C%2048%25%20of%20surveyed%20desk%20workers%20said%20they%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Buncomfortable%26quot%3B%20admitting%20to%20their%20manager%20that%20they're%20using%20AI%20for%20at%20least%20one%20of%20those%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20said%20they%20were%20concerned%20that%20bosses%20may%20view%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bless%20competent%26quot%3B%20or%20lazy%2C%20and%2047%25%20said%20they%20fel