p%20with%20nasscom%20foundation%20and%20open%20it%20to%20universities%20across%20the%20country%20to%20promote%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20encompasses%20a%20four-stage%20programme%2C%20nurturing%20the%20transformation%20of%20ideas%20into%20thriving%20ventures.%20From%20the%20ideation%20stage%20to%20incubation%2C%20the%20top%2010%20teams%20are%20granted%20a%20seed%20fund%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20marking%20the%20transition%20of%20their%20social%20ventures%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seventh%20edition%20of%20thingQbator%20is%20currently%20underway%2C%20mentoring%20and%20nurturing%20undergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20students%20with%20a%20vision%20aligned%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%E2%80%99%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20incubating%20new%20startups%2C%20thingQbator%20also%20offers%20a%20myriad%20of%20learning%20opportunities%20for%20students%20across%20the%20country.%20This%20learning%20platform%20offers%20over%2018%20courses%20in%20hardware%20and%20software%20that%20students%20can%20complete%20at%20their%20convenience%20to%20enhance%20their%20technical%20skills.%20This%20platform%20is%20available%20to%20all%20students%20who%20register.%20The%20courses%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%20%E2%80%94%20from%20building%20apps%20using%20Flutter%20to%20creating%20websites%2C%20web%20development%20skills%2C%20and%20working%20with%20Raspberry%20Pi%203%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20a%20high%20level%20of%20technical%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2030%2C000%20course%20completion%20certificates%20have%20been%20issued%2C%20and%20over%2016%2C000%20unique%20students%20have%20received%20course%20completion%20certificates%20as%20of%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20providing%20a%20platform%20that%20transcends%20entrepreneurial%20incubation%2C%20thingQbator%20is%20empowering%20young%20Indians%20to%20become%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20technology%20and%20innovation.