a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F465035090_2074855469618513_8670123272276526198_n-1730899273.jpg%20720w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-374772%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESavita%20Sunil%20Dakle%20uses%20her%20extensive%20experience%20in%20sustainable%20agriculture%20to%20train%20women%20in%20organic%20farming%20through%20her%20online%20community%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Savita%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Faditya.dakle.1htrhrhrt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20can%20protect%20crops%20by%20using%20mulching%20techniques%2C%20which%20help%20warm%20the%20soil%2C%20and%20by%20covering%20plants%20with%20frost%20blankets%20or%20plastic%20sheets%20to%20reduce%20frost%20exposure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Retain%20moisture%20with%20mulching%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20regions%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20winter%20often%20brings%20drier%20conditions%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20reduced%20soil%20moisture.%20While%20cool%20weather%20reduces%20evaporation%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20rainfall%20can%20still%20dry%20out%20soils%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20crops%20to%20access%20water.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20black%20or%20clayey%20soil%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20retain%20moisture%2C%20softer%20soils%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20so%20farmers%20should%20understand%20their%20soil%20type%20and%20plan%20accordingly%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Savita.%20Farmers%20can%20use%20mulches%20to%20help%20retain%20moisture%20and%20apply%20water%20conservation%20techniques%20like%20drip%20irrigation%20or%20rainwater%20harvesting%20to%20ensu